snippet.textDisplay:
Instructor here. I love how the coach is very encouraging and informative, I usually give shorter introductions and slowly teach everything else end by end, but in a similar case to this with media involve I give a longer one which take safety and rules more seriously.


And as a person with depression, your mood and mentality does greatly affect your performance, if you linger on the bad shots you made it's really difficult to keep focus. And to keep in mind that you should learn from your bad shots and forget about it really helps me in daily life.


cheers to y'all
snippet.textOriginal:
Instructor here. I love how the coach is very encouraging and informative, I usually give shorter introductions and slowly teach everything else end by end, but in a similar case to this with media involve I give a longer one which take safety and rules more seriously.
